title: Reaching
body:
read it on the AO3 at http://bit.ly/2v4UDFD

by Nanna_Jemima

Reaching the end of one’s tether, reaching too far, and reaching out. Tony’s used to the first two. The last one, though. That’s a tough bastard. Post-Civil War final battle thoughts. Please note Civil War ending is AU and is detailed in the previous work in this series.

summary: not to take credit or anything but all I’m saying is when Infinity War first came out, I said that the reason they couldn’t have...
body:
not to take credit or anything but all I’m saying is when Infinity War first came out, I said that the reason they couldn’t have AntMan show up is because he would’ve ended things so much sooner by expanding in thanos’s ass, and Disney clearly wanted to profit off two films.

now all of a sudden all these memes are poppin up and…… I’m just sayin

body:
*watching CA: TWS*


*Pierce gets orange juice out of fridge, sees the Asset, pours himself the world’s tiniest glass of milk instead, leaves orange juice container out bc he is terrible*


*Sam Wilson finishes his run, grabs a bottle of orange juice from the fridge, but is interrupted by Steve and Natasha knocking at his door before he can take a sip*


my husband: god, no one in this movie can ever get their orange juice


It’s my new favorite thing. No one in the MCU can ever get their orange juice. 😂
